article.description: — Ty Gadsden had 21 points as UNC Wilmington rolled past Delaware State 87-63 on Wednesday.
article.headline: Gadsden carries UNC-Wilmington over Delaware State 87-63
article.linkText: Gadsden carries UNC-Wilmington over Delaware State 87-63
article.story: WILMINGTON, N.C. -- — Ty Gadsden had 21 points as UNC Wilmington rolled past Delaware State 87-63 on Wednesday. Jaylen Sims had 15 points for UNCW (6-3). Joe Pridgen added 14 points and 10 rebounds, and Jake Boggs had 11 points. Zach Kent had 15 points for the Hornets (0-4). Pinky Wiley and Omari Peek-Green each had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
